_sText:
This version of de.dust2.unlimited is just a fps optimized map for the [CS:S DM Plugin (SourceMod)](http://www.bailopan.net/cssdm/index.php?page=download "CS:S DM Plugin (SourceMod)"). 

NoBlock required - Clips are removed (95%)


- 70% decals removed
- 20% textures removed
- 10% brushes removed
- 95% clips removed
- all physical objects removed
- buy-zones & bomb-zones removed
- new spawn spots (safer for DM)
- ambient-sounds removed
- smoke slowed down & particel reduced
- optimized light environment
- new tunnel created (screenshots)
